HEADWORD: Lyginopteridales
<hw>Lyginopteridales</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>An order of fossil
gymnospermous trees or climbing plants from the Devonian: the seed
ferns.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Cycadofilicales, order <ord>Cycadofilicales</ord>,
order <ord>Lyginopteridales</ord>.</syn>⟦br⟧
